@startuml sequence-complete-workflow
skinparam dpi 150
skinparam pageMargin 10
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title Full Lifecycle: New -> Received -> Started -> Completed

actor Member
actor Staff
participant "MaintenanceRequest\nController" as Ctrl
participant "Handlers" as H
participant "MaintenanceRequest\n(Aggregate)" as Agg
database "CoopDbContext" as DB

== 1. Create (Member) ==
Member -> Ctrl : POST /api/MaintenanceRequest
Ctrl -> H : CreateMaintenanceRequestHandler
H -> Agg ** : new MaintenanceRequest(event)
note right : **Status = New**
H -> DB : Add + SaveChanges
Ctrl --> Member : 200 OK

== 2. Receive (Staff) ==
Staff -> Ctrl : PUT /api/MaintenanceRequest/receive
Ctrl -> H : ReceiveMaintenanceRequestHandler
H -> DB : Load aggregate
H -> Agg : Apply(ReceiveMaintenanceRequest)
note right : **Status = Received**\nReceivedByProfileId\nReceivedByName
H -> DB : SaveChanges
Ctrl --> Staff : 200 OK

== 3. Start (Staff) ==
Staff -> Ctrl : PUT /api/MaintenanceRequest/start
Ctrl -> H : StartMaintenanceRequestHandler
H -> DB : Load aggregate
H -> Agg : Apply(StartMaintenanceRequest)
note right : **Status = Started**\nWorkStarted timestamp\nUnitEntered value
H -> DB : SaveChanges
Ctrl --> Staff : 200 OK

== 4. Complete (Staff) ==
Staff -> Ctrl : PUT /api/MaintenanceRequest/complete
Ctrl -> H : CompleteMaintenanceRequestHandler
H -> DB : Load aggregate
H -> Agg : Apply(CompleteMaintenanceRequest)
note right : **Status = Completed**\nWorkCompleted timestamp\nWorkCompletedByName
H -> DB : SaveChanges
Ctrl --> Staff : 200 OK
@enduml
